::Battera::

She flew around untill her mind was clearer. She flew back to the Destron 
base.  She landed and transformed into bot mode.  She still had that devise 
that Cybershark gave her.  She walked in the front door and looked around.  
What made her decide to even return her, she didn't know.  She kept a wary 
eye out for anything that might be a trap.  She still didn't trust anyone at 
this point.
